			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Leave camp or equip the amulet after using successfully using the amulet's unique ability multiple times during the previous day\r\n\r\nRepro steps to get the amulet:\r\n1. Start the game\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. goto -626 224\r\n4. Unlock the Adamantine chest\r\n5. Take the amulet.\r\n\r\nRepro steps:\r\n1. Get the amulet\r\n2. Use the ability multiple times.\r\n3. Go to Camp.\r\n4. Fully rest and leave camp.\r\n5. Equip or stow amulet."
				},
