				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Player has left the camp. A few moments later, they are overcome with an unnatural sense of cheer. If they fail the check, they will fall over in laughter every time they use the amulet's special power that day.\r\n\r\nThe madness has several levels."
